survey_response.review_text: This was my first gynaecologist experience and it was bad . Doctor didn’t wear mask, she wasn’t even wearing gloves . First of all , the fees is 500 on practo and if you directly go to the clinic it’s 300. I was already so nervous, she didn’t even inform me before inserting the device inside me . And that device is definitely huge. I think she should have informed me. After that she assumed that i was sexually active I don’t know what she saw in there but i said no i am not sexually active . I was but i am not anymore it’s been 4-5 months . I don’t know if this how you treat a patient . I think you can’t straight away insert something without informing the patient.
